Lambda Best Practices
- make handler a unit-testable function
- reusability
- decouple
- environment variables
- package dependencies with deployment package
- minimize package size to runtime necessities
- no recursion

Function Configuration
- performance testing - max memory used
- load testing - how long does the function run
- restrict permissions
- what are the lambda limits
- delete functions not in use
- SQS visibility timeout >= function execution time

